  "keyFeatures": [
    "Unified inbox connecting Gmail, Outlook, and other email providers",
    "AI-powered email composition and smart replies",
    "Self-hosting with Docker and Cloudflare Workers support",
    "Privacy-first architecture — no data tracking or selling",
    "MCP (Model Context Protocol) integration for AI tooling",
    "Custom labels, categories, and filters",
    "Keyboard shortcuts and customizable UI",
